headline: Businesses are Cutting AI Tools, Not Budgets -- beefed.ai Offers the Specialist Alternative
summary: Enterprise spending on artificial intelligence is rising, but the number of AI vendors companies use is shrinking. Businesses are increasing AI budgets in 2026 while signing fewer contracts — consolidating around tools that deliver measurable results in specific domains.

headline: Analyzing the Evolving Earnings Picture: What Should Investors Know?
